name: Women's Grizzly Bear T-Shirt
description:
Awwww...little teddy bear wants to be your friend! 

Actually, grizzly bears are found throughout North America and can reach weights up to 1,000 pounds! They are omnivores and primarily solitarily active. But now you can take one with you wherever you go...

Brown grizzly bear is hand-screened onto a soft, 100% cotton creme-colored t-shirt. 

American Apparel fine jersey tee in size LARGE.

name: Women's Bobcat T-Shirt
description:
Rrrrawr! This baby bobcat is mad...or maybe just feisty. But still totally adorable! Sound like anyone you know?

Brown bobcat is hand-screened onto a soft, 100% cotton creme-colored American Apparel t-shirt. Polka dots of pink, yellow, green, blue, white, orange, red and brown surround.

Each shirt is hand printed and unique, so color and placement of dots will vary.
